I have been visit them and buy gospel books &material since 20 years ago. Pastor and staffs there are humble servants. Sell gifts in affordable price , so that we can buy more;
Some people will donate some books too and they give for free. Will support always !
Received a weird pamphlet about "DEATH is like moving house" preaching about death. What the hell.
It's a place for the Godly and spiritually minded,  who wants to put God's Kingdom first before self.
bookstore with resources for the church.
